languages.text: "Солдаты Бога-Императора! Кому еще уши мешают слушать?! Шаг вперед, обрежу!"
"I said you're soldiers of the God-Emperor! Which one of you has a problem with your ears? Step forward and I'll cut them off!"

traits.locale_text: “神皇的士兵们！你们的耳朵有毛病吗？要是谁耳朵有毛病，立刻出列，我把他耳朵砍下来！”

languages.text: 「聞け、神帝陛下の兵士ども！耳に問題のあるやつはどいつだ？前へ出ろ！切り落としてやる！」
languages.original_text: "I said you're soldiers of the God-Emperor! Which one of you has a problem with your ears? Step forward and I'll cut them off!"

traits.locale_text: 「聞け、神帝陛下の兵士ども！耳に問題のあるやつはどいつだ？前へ出ろ！切り落としてやる！」

languages.text: « J'ai dit que vous étiez des soldats de l'Empereur-Dieu ! Vous êtes un peu durs de la feuille ? Approchez, je vais vous déboucher les oreilles, moi ! »
languages.original_text: "I said you're soldiers of the God-Emperor! Which one of you has a problem with your ears? Step forward and I'll cut them off!"

traits.locale_text: « Soldats de l'Empereur-Dieu ! Vous êtes un peu durs de la feuille ? Approchez, je vais vous déboucher les oreilles, moi ! »

languages.text: «¡He dicho que sois soldados del Dios Emperador! ¿Estáis sordos o qué? ¡Dad un paso adelante y os cortaré las orejas para oír mejor!».
languages.original_text: "I said you're soldiers of the God-Emperor! Which one of you has a problem with your ears? Step forward and I'll cut them off!"

traits.locale_text: «¡Soldados del Dios Emperador! ¿Estáis sordos o qué? ¡Dad un paso adelante y os cortaré las orejas para oír mejor!».

languages.text: "Ich sagte, Ihr seid Soldaten des Gottimperators! Wer von Euch hat Probleme mit den Ohren? Tretet vor, dann schneide ich sie ab!"
languages.original_text: "I said you're soldiers of the God-Emperor! Which one of you has a problem with your ears? Step forward and I'll cut them off!"

traits.locale_text: "Soldaten des Gottimperators! Wer von Euch hat ein Problem mit seinen Ohren? Tretet vor, dann schneide ich sie Euch ab!"

languages.text: "Tanrı İmparator'un askerlerisiniz dedim! Aranızda kulağı duymayan var mı? Öne çıksın da keseyim kulaklarını!"
